{"tid":580281,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"007擔任頒獎人走樣膠臉","createTime":"2018-03-04T11:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T12:26:16.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad512b35cb666aaf6d21cd9341e0b9dd64f27781","tid":580281,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"「007」丹尼爾克雷格向來帥氣逼人，儘管當初接下龐德一角時不被外界看好，但現在他可是全球粉絲心中最帥龐德代表！只是近來他現身公開活動，不僅臉蛋比過去圓潤許多，還被指「塑膠感」很重，讓人不禁懷疑他是否「修修臉」！<br />\n<br />\n丹尼爾克雷格日前到英國影藝學院電影獎擔任頒獎人，只是事後他的外型卻在網上造成轟動討論，不少網友紛紛標註「丹尼爾克雷格的臉發生什麼事？」全因過去帥氣的臉蛋，如今胖了一圈，加上極不自然的緊繃被說塑膠感很重，就被質疑他是否去整形微調。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-02-22/656/20180222001300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-02-22%2F656%2F20180222001300.jpg&h=d4252267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1fef23adb7983a9ac3aa253632963b7f27204d2","tid":580281,"uid":40801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:23:34.000Z","msg":"嘩、屌、之前好L型。"},{"pid":"8687647c2ddeffd0a296225e9bc49a84c5ce2637","tid":580281,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"兩個人黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cab53b4c537c0f5791f26b09afe11767f4f765","tid":580281,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"肥咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846ae5edef0c55b9e35e4b4c8e009f0e0ef00346","tid":580281,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"一早已經話佢係Illuminati控制嘅蜥蜴人，而家冇得否認"},{"pid":"8bf83c6ade70d171de9d2f4c618e541faaafd615","tid":580281,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"